@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mocogf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.17 * v0 + 0.48)) - wp.sin(v1))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.51) - 0.53) * wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp + 0.59)))
    v2 = v1
    v2 = v2
    tmp = wp.exp(0.24)
    data[tid] = v0
